  <slide>
    <hgroup>
      <h2>Collective Communications I</h2>
    </hgroup>
    <article>
      <ul>
	<li>Communication performed in all processes in the communicator</li>
	<li>Used when communication among all processes is wanted, in substitution of point-to-point operations</li>
	<li>Message tags are not used</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </slide>
  <slide>
    <hgroup>
      <h2>Collective Function Types</h2>
    </hgroup>
    <article>
      <ul>
	<li>Syncronization</li>
	<ul><li>To Syncronize the processers</li></ul>
	<li>Data Movement</li>
	<ul><li>To distribute or collect the data</li></ul>
	<li>Computation</li>
	<ul><li>Each processor performs an operation to the data in place</li></ul>
       <ul>
    </article>
  </slide>
  
  <slide>
    <hgroup>
      <h2>MPI_Scatter</h2>
	
	
    </hgroup>
    <article>
   <p><pre class="prettyprint" data-lang="c">int MPI_Scatter(void* sbuf, int scount, MPI_Datatype stype, void*
rbuf, int rcount, MPI_Datatype rtype, int root, MPI_Comm comm)</pre></p>
	<ul>
	 <li>The process with rank==<b>root</b> splits the buffer and sends to the other processors in order: First part to the first processor, etc</li>
	 <li><b>sbuf</b>: The buffer to split and send</li>
	 <li><b>scount</b>: The size of each part</li>
	 <li><b>rbuf</b>: The variable were the part for each processor is stored</li>
	 <li><b>rcount</b>: The size of the data to recieve</li>
	</ul> 
  </article>
  </slide>

  <slide>
    <hgroup>
      <h2>MPI_Gather</h2>
	
	
    </hgroup>
    <article>
   <p><pre class="prettyprint" data-lang="c">int MPI_Gather(void* sbuf, int scount, MPI_Datatype stype, void*
rbuf, int rcount, MPI_Datatype rtype, int root, MPI_Comm comm)</pre></p>
	<ul>
	 <li>Each processor with rank!=<b>root</b> send the buffer to the<b>root</b>,that collects all the data</li>
	 <li><b>sbuf</b>: The buffer to send for each processor</li>
	 <li><b>scount</b>: The size of the data to send</li>
	 <li><b>rbuf</b>: The variable were the part for each processor is stored in the <b>root</b></li>
	 <li><b>rcount</b>:The size of each part recieved</li>
	</ul> 
  </article>
  </slide>
  <slide>
    <hgroup>
      <h2>MPI_Scatter,MPI_Gather example</h2>
